{"tid":37622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國務卿親俄】「美俄聯手牽制中國」 大陸商界好擔心","createTime":"2016-12-13T12:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T08:54:29.000Z","uid":62257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ba75ae4adad6b7fa254a2cfc03ba7672a1c9932","tid":37622,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:33:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161213&amp;guid=56041075&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161213%26guid%3D56041075%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=Z6mWvjkh4U%2FzXuqpUJjLFHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=81bf991b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161213%26guid%3D56041075%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=a3bddf19\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161213&amp;guid=56041075&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒報道，總統當選人特朗普將提名埃克森美孚行政總裁蒂勒森（Rex Tillerson）出任國務卿，蒂勒森與俄羅斯總統普京關係密切，北京商界人士深感困惑，擔心特朗普將與俄羅斯聯手牽制中國，「迫中國出局」。<br />\n<br />\n「噢是的，他與（俄羅斯總統）普京有交情。」中國的石油公司高層說，他們對蒂勒森一點也不陌生，更熟知埃克森美孚的動向，「他1990年代起便與俄羅斯合作發展石油及（庫頁島）天然氣場，人人都知道他與普京很熟」。<br />\n<br />\n油企高層正加緊分析特朗普上任後對中國的影響，內地商界石油公司高層坦言：「這肯定意味着俄羅斯及美國將會變得更密切，這是否代表中國被踢出局了？」<br />\n<br />\n另一位中國油企高層則認為，「蒂勒森與普京就像是強人相遇」，他指蒂勒森若然當上美國國務卿，是讓「強人在管理國際事務」。<br />\n<br />\n埃克森美孚在中國及香港都有業務，與中國淵源可以追溯至1890年代。外媒相信蒂勒森一旦當上國務卿，中方會小心監察美俄關係的微妙變化。<br />\n<br />\n雅虎財經"},{"pid":"0700993ec7e8654758f5ac3d58b66fa3c1e99ba5","tid":37622,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510f509469c851567e23705c2407a4e96432ddd5","tid":37622,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc0aa89c857fb41dca5a2cc717df9ba083a4dfe","tid":37622,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:42:04.000Z","msg":"某弱國要怕了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268bae0d9a91b54ea1ef27f4d396505dcbafd04c","tid":37622,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:04:07.000Z","msg":"要不是支那，地球那會轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1472cbfa7860dd33499ce1a283ac9ceca9c35b","tid":37622,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"美俄聯盟共抗法西斯中國"},{"pid":"cc0a9f8de418ce1f151f7277cf37f54f14da0497","tid":37622,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a213f887460ef2a796129656db02ec5c5cd2b95f","tid":37622,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:44:25.000Z","msg":"有大戲睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da69249115ae38e5c244a988baffc0d8a8e95e9f","tid":37622,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:10:12.000Z","msg":"點解成日話打日本打台灣<br />\n唔打埋俄佬呢?"},{"pid":"386ab3eeae1e25e6968d4aecd9f8b67297a05511","tid":37622,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:19:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解成日話打日本打台灣<br />\n唔打埋俄佬呢?</blockquote><br />\n契哥邊敢嘈"},{"pid":"5e52fb95ed4fca683ee56c22ae9ce283ab4fc892","tid":37622,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:56:25.000Z","msg":"原本認為係涼戰，點知turn out係八國聯軍"},{"pid":"ff07fbe14e00487f5160559b44980b65c4c59a4f","tid":37622,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T18:58:03.000Z","msg":"俄佬hack左美帝<br />\n然後用美帝打中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664c820bca34d1dde157e55a3e43856b4fc63b4c","tid":37622